title: Savory Maza
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Delivery, Take-out, Lebanese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A casual restaurant with many vegan choices including spinach pie, grape leaves, hummus, falafel, tabouli, veggie kibbee b'saneyeh and more, including a dessert. Al, the owner, will be happy to go over all ingredients and guide you to the many vegan dishes. BYOB.
